              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "238UF4 targets were prepared by evaporation of UF4 onto",
                " 0.58 mg/cm2 arc-shaped Al backing foils. Nine of the",
                " UF4 target segments were arranged on the periphery of",
                " a 35-cm diameter target wheel located approximately 1",
                " cm downstream of the carbon entrance window"
              ]
            }
          ],
